Interface IBswModuleDependency

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable

    public interface IBswModuleDependency
extends IEntity, IIdentifiable
    IBswModuleDependency: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This class collects the dependencies of a BSW module or cluster on a certain other BSW module.

      • getServiceItems

        java.util.Map<java.lang.String,? extends IServiceNeeds> getServiceItems()
        Query the bidirectional identifiable aggregation serviceItem.

        A single item (example: Nv block) for which the quality of a service is defined. The aggregation is marked as <<atpSplitable>> to allow for extension during the ECU configuration process. This association is deprecated since R4.0.3, since ServiceNeeds shall be associated with the new element BswServiceDependency within the BswInternalBehavior.

        the referenced entities
